[03:32.73]When you rise at the first chirping of the birds
[03:44.18]Before you near the grave and everlasting your home
[04:03.72]INTERLUDE
VERSE 5
[04:46.28]Remember your God, my dear friend
[04:58.38]Life as you know it, precious and beautiful
[05:09.36]Will come to an end and you’ll say
[05:20.20]My life was a vapor! What did I do for my creator?
VAMP
